Epigenetic modification of miR-217 promotes intervertebral disc degeneration by targeting the FBXO21-ERK signalling pathway.
Overexpression of miR-217 inhibits IDD via FBXO21/ERK regulation.
Pubmed   Journal   ReadQx 
Four emerging immune cellular blood phenotypes associated with disease duration and activity established in Psoriatic Arthritis.
 Four immune cellular phenotypes of PsA were suggested at baseline demonstrating complex immune cellular mechanisms in PsA implying the possibility of improving PsA patient stratification based on both clinical and immune cellular phenotypes.
Pubmed   Journal   ReadQx 
Arthritis Rheumatol
    Impaired efferocytosis by synovial macrophages in patients with knee osteoarthritis.
 Apoptotic cells accumulate in the synovium of patients with late-stage knee OA. Our results suggest that OA impairs critical homeostatic functions of synovial macrophages leading to accumulation of apoptotic cells.
